df84			; Which startup method to use? 
df84			; 
df84			; version 1 - allows for a single stored file to be selected to run at start up (if se storage is enabled) 
df84			; followed by loading of a list of scripts in eeprom 
df84			 
df84			; version 2 - if se storage is enabled then auto load all files which begin with a '*' else use loading 
df84			; from eeprom 
